```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start[Start inner loop] --> CheckPending{Có pendingMessages?}
    CheckPending -->|Có| Inject[Inject pending messages<br/>push message_start/end, add to context]
    CheckPending -->|Không| Stream

    Inject --> Stream[Stream assistant response]
    
    Stream --> Transform[transformContext (optional)]
    Transform --> Convert[convertToLlm]
    Convert --> LLM[LLM call via streamSimple]
    LLM --> Build[Build AssistantMessage]
    Build --> HasTools{Assistant có<br/>tool calls?}
    
    HasTools -->|Có| Exec[executeToolCalls()]
    Exec --> LoopTools{Vòng lặp tools<br/>sequential}
    LoopTools --> ToolStart[tool_execution_start]
    ToolStart --> Validate[validateToolArguments]
    Validate --> Execute[tool.execute()]
    Execute --> HasUpdate{Có onUpdate?}
    HasUpdate -->|Có| ToolUpdate[tool_execution_update]
    HasUpdate -->|Không| AfterExec
    AfterExec --> ToolEnd[tool_execution_end]
    ToolEnd --> CreateResult[Tạo ToolResultMessage]
    CreateResult --> PushToolMsg[push message_start/end<br/>(toolResult)]
    PushToolMsg --> CheckSteering{Check steering<br/>sau mỗi tool}
    CheckSteering -->|Có| SetSteering[Set pendingMessages = steering]
    CheckSteering -->|Không| NextTool{Next tool?}
    SetSteering --> SkipRest[Skip remaining tools<br/>via skipToolCall]
    SkipRest --> Break[Break tool loop]
    NextTool -->|Còn| LoopTools
    NextTool -->|Hết| AfterTools
    
    AfterTools --> TurnEnd[push turn_end]
    HasTools -->|Không| TurnEnd
    
    TurnEnd --> CheckSteerNow{Check steering<br/>lại sau turn?}
    CheckSteerNow -->|Có| SetPending[Set pendingMessages = steering]
    CheckSteerNow -->|Không| GetSteering[getSteeringMessages?]
    GetSteering -->|Có| SetPending
    GetSteering -->|Không| EndInner[Inner loop kết thúc<br/>(pendingMessages empty, no tools)]

    SetPending --> EndInner

    EndInner --> OuterCheck{Outer loop check<br/>follow-up}
    OuterCheck -->|Có| OuterCont[Outer loop tiếp tục<br/>pendingMessages = follow-up]
    OuterCheck -->|Không| Done[Done → agent_end]
```

---

**Legend**:
- Inner loop xử lý một turn: assistant response + tools (nếu có).
- Steering check sau mỗi tool và sau turn.
- Nếu steering có, pendingMessages được set, inner loop tiếp tục ngay (turn mới).
- Outer loop chỉ check follow-up sau khi inner loop kết thúc (không còn tools, không có pending messages).
